CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 24, 1965, pg. 6 reads: "Mr. and Mrs. William A. Bauknight Jr....leaving church - Harris Photo." Portion of accompanying article reads: "In a solemn morning ceremony on July 10, lovely Barbara Ann Williams became the bride of William A. Bauknight Jr. The bride is the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Charles F. Williams of Blackadore St.  The groom is the son of Mr. and Mrs. W.A. Bauknight Sr., of East Orange, N.J.  The Rev. Father Charles Cherdini of Mother of Good Counsel Church, officiated at the ceremony which was followed by an evening reception in beautiful gardens of the McClainey Estate on Wilkinsburg Ave."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of bride Barbara Ann Williams Bauknight and groom William A. Bauknight Jr. seated inside car
